Sentencas: A metal-supported SOFC with a samarium doped ceria (SDC)/scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) bilayer electrolyte was fabricated by a combination of pulsed laser deposition (PLD) and wet ceramic processes.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cell operated at 400-600°C

Sentencas: The cell performance and aging characteristics during operation were analyzed by both AC impedance spectroscopy and current-voltage measurements in the temperature range from 400 degrees C to 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cell operated at 400-600°C

Sentencas: The power generation characteristics of this metal-supported SOFC at low temperatures should allow for rapid start-up and help to reduce the performance deterioration seen in high temperature SOFCs due material oxidation and instability.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cell operated at 400-600°C

Sentencas: In this paper, our early research results are presented.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cell operated at 400-600°C
